  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 2217948139912429689
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 1d4486ec-8b1e-4514-a4bc-5f9e95f77bcf
        Position: {x: 982, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Incase you haven't read it elsewhere, your whole purpose is to
          make mutation of plants. After sequencing them in a computer, you can print
          the seed using a <i>Biological Printer</i>.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429690
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 4000a8aa-76ba-4314-a161-95f2d6a9ffad
        Position: {x: 1355, y: -68}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Inspired by stardew valley, you must garden your new seedlings.
          I had no good reason in the lore... I mean sending the seeds back right
          away seems smarter.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429691
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: d1edd06e-356f-46a5-91cc-ed3c9a1cfc78
        Position: {x: 1355, y: 195}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: The shuttle in room 1 isn't for people, your on a one way trip
          to save earth of course!
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429692
      type: {class: EndNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: d285ca70-11fc-4ad8-a444-6f770c8a3e79
        Position: {x: 1404, y: 789}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429693
      type: {class: DialogOptionsNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: a0cdd2aa-f0a6-420c-b749-d47385ea76ef
        Position: {x: 682, y: 303}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: I'll let you choose, I reccomend reading up on <b>World Lore</b>
          first.
        ResponseOptions:
        - Computer Info
        - Biological Printer
        - Gardens
        - Shuttle
        - World Lore
        - Exit
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429694
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: a47d359e-5fd5-4851-a964-b74183c2cd6c
        Position: {x: 1724, y: 195}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: It ships your grown plantsback to earth! A specalized pod drop
          fast enough to dig into the ground, perfectly planting your new mutant
          plant.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429695
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 84a69975-4ebf-4461-aaad-e1a72995c22b
        Position: {x: 1371, y: 470}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: To keep it fairly short, in the far future a virus wipes out
          almost all living plants. This was known as the <b>Sparaxis</b> (which
          I named after a real <color=#FF58AC>flower</color>)
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429696
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: b51f5e81-fb62-44c3-bd40-d686e2051a01
        Position: {x: 1724, y: 502}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: 'With the last resources of earths civilization, they sent a
          lone researcher to develop resistant plant mutants away from the disease. '
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429697
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 319316d3-ed5b-4b79-8129-377c8d5b864a
        Position: {x: 2099, y: 502}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Game cycle would only have been about 30 minutes, each root gave
          extra percent and increased the world recovery rate. (like plague inc.
          lol)
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429698
      type: {class: StartNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 96225873-99a3-41b9-8c3f-e22c02af87cc
        Position: {x: -592, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429699
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: ac906ae5-b927-4e83-899b-357b6a3a3f02
        Position: {x: -122, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: This game is incomplete :( Though it has working core functionality.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429700
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 279a6aec-e3ca-412c-aec6-a86510abc732
        Position: {x: -459, y: -164}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Welcome to the <color=#EF32FF>Help Desk!</color> where I will
          explain some parts of the game.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429701
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: b42fff2d-00bf-4f3e-a74a-8b5a19b504e2
        Position: {x: 1228, y: -657}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: Eventually, the planet become green again and the infection called
          <b>Sparaxis</b>, which is killing all plants will be gone. More on Sparaxis
          in my world lore.
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429702
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 0e725733-429e-428e-b1b8-9aae366dd4bf
        Position: {x: 602, y: -284}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: 'A computer allows you to <i>Sequence</i>. This is a little minigame
          representing your mutation of a plants DNA! '
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
    - rid: 2217948139912429703
      type: {class: DialogNodeData, ns: NodeTree, asm: Hiileike.Nodetree}
      data:
        Guid: 8da055c8-4f1b-437e-8b82-b2e9fc19370e
        Position: {x: 908, y: -498}
        HasSeen: 0
        Conditions: []
        ConditionFailBehavior: 0
        DialogText: After mutating the DNA, you can print a new seedling at the <b>Biological
          Printer</b>. After growing it in a <b>Garden</b>, you can send it back
          to earth in a <b>Shuttle</b>!
        TypingTickClip: {fileID: 0}
        FontAsset: {fileID: 0}
        FontSize: 36
        FontColor: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
        FontStyle: 0
        TextSpeed: 0
